pesticide.PPE: Long sleeved shirt and long pants; Shoes plus socks; Waterproof gloves
pesticide.product_use: AGRICULTURAL, CANNABIS, GREENHOUSE, HEMP, NURSERY, ORNAMENTAL

Safety_Information.general_Info: CAUTION: Harmful if absorbed through skin. Causes moderate eye irritation. Avoid contact with skin, eyes or clothing. Wash thoroughly with soap and water after handling this product.
Safety_Information.if_In_Eyes: Hold eye open and rinse slowly and gently with water for 15-20 minutes; Remove contact lenses after the first 5 minutes, then continue rinsing; Call Poison Control Center or doctor for treatment advice.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: Have the product container or label with you when calling a Poison Control Center or doctor, or going for treatment.
Safety_Information.if_On_Skin: Take off contaminated clothing and immediately rinse skin with plenty of water for 15-20 minutes; Call Poison Control Center or doctor for treatment advice.
